data.title: Back in The USSA
data.meta_description: Back in the USSA - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides acknowledgments and credits for characters that were sampled in the stories. It thanks various people for their support, advice, inspiration and technical help. It also lists over 100 characters that were sampled and remixed from films, books, TV shows and other works in creating the stories.
